# GITHUB SECRETS NECESARIOS PARA CI/CD
# Configurar en GitHub > Settings > Secrets and variables > Actions

# === RAILWAY DEPLOYMENT ===
RAILWAY_TOKEN=your-railway-api-token-here

# === SMTP CREDENTIALS (para testing en CI) ===
SMTP_USER=tu-email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=tu-app-password-gmail

# === OPTIONAL: ANALYTICS ===
VITE_ANALYTICS_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# === CÓMO OBTENER RAILWAY_TOKEN ===
# 1. Ir a https://railway.app/account/tokens
# 2. Crear nuevo token con permisos de deployment
# 3. Copiar el token generado
# 4. Agregarlo como secret en GitHub

# === CÓMO CONFIGURAR EN GITHUB ===
# 1. Ir a tu repositorio en GitHub
# 2. Settings > Secrets and variables > Actions
# 3. New repository secret para cada variable
# 4. Nombre: RAILWAY_TOKEN, Value: tu-token-railway
